\c 30
\s Rwiyo rwokuvonga
\d Pisarema; rwiyo pakutsaurira Jehovha imba; Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 3 o
\v 1 Ndichakukudzai zvikuru, Jehovha;
\s nokuti makandisimudza,
\s Hamuna kutendera vavengi vangu kufara nokuda kwangu.
\p
\v 2 Jehovha, Mwari wangu, Ndakachema kwamuri, imi mukandiponesa.
\p
\v 3 Jehovha, makabudisa mweya
\s wangu paSheori;
\s Makachengeta upenyu hwangu, kuti ndirege kuburukira kugomba.
\p
\v 4 Imbirai Jehovha nziyo
\s dzokurumbidza,
\s imi vatsvene vake,
\s Muvonge kana muchirangarira zita rake dzvene.
\p
\v 5 Nokuti kutsamwa kwake kuripo chinguva chiduku;
\s Asi ngoni dzake ndedzoupenyu hwose.
\p Kuchema kungavapo madekwana, Asi mufaro unosvika mangwanani.
\v 6 Kana ndirini, ndakati pakufara
\s kwangu, "Handingatongozununguswi."
\p
\v 7 Imi Jehovha, nengoni dzenyu makamisa gomo rangu nesimba; Makavanza chiso chenyu; ini
\s ndikatambudzika.
\p
\v 8 Ndakachema kwamuri, Jehovha; Uye ndakakumbira kuna Jehovha;
\v 9 "Ropa rangu ringandibatsireiko, kana ndichaburukira kugomba? Guruva ringakurumbidzai here?
\s Ringadudzira zvokwadi yenyu here?
\s lo Inzwai Jehovha, mundinzwirei tsitsi; Jehovha, ivai mubatsiri wangu."
\p
\v 11 Makashandura kuchema kwangu kukava kutamba;
\s Makasunungura gumbo rangu, mukasunga chiuno changu nomufaro;
\p
\v 12 Kuti mweya wangu ukuimbirei nziyo dzokurumbidza, urege kunyarara.
\s Jehovha Mwari wangu, ndichakuvongai nokusingaperi.
